      <p style="font-family: Inter, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.75; color: #444444; margin: 0 0 24px 0; max-width: 720px;">Cheshire's 11 main property market towns split into three survey categories based on dominant housing stock and location-specific risks. The map and table below map each town to its recommended survey level, primary construction type, and the specific defects a surveyor prioritises in that area.</p>
      
